title: Kim Kardashian Shares Cute Photos of North West Strolling Around Pumpkin Patch
text:
Comments North and her 'BFF' Ryan Romulus, the daughter of designer Tracy Nguyen Romulus, look adorable in some snaps taken when Kim took the girls to the pumpkin patch. 
Kim Kardashian is getting into the Halloween spirit and she makes sure her daughter North West is too. The reality TV star recently took her little girl to a pumpkin patch and she shared some cute pictures from the outing via Instagram on Monday, October 19. Also joining Kim and her daughter on the trip was the tot's "BFF" Ryan Romulus, the daughter of designer Tracy Nguyen Romulus. In one snap the 34-year-old star posted, North and Ryan are walking hand in hand with their backs facing the camera. A photo posted by Kim Kardashian West (@kimkardashian) on Oct 19, 2015 at 12:17pm PDT Another photo shows the girls sitting on pumpkins while sporting face painting. "Bff's at the pumpkin patch," Kim wrote in the caption. The last picture of the two were taken while they were sleeping in the car. "Knocked out!" the " Keeping Up with the Kardashians " star said. A photo posted by Kim Kardashian West (@kimkardashian) on Oct 19, 2015 at 1:17pm PDT A photo posted by Kim Kardashian West (@kimkardashian) on Oct 19, 2015 at 3:36pm PDT Kim is fresh off returning to L.A. after visiting Lamar Odom in Las Vegas. Last week, she and her family rushed to the former NBA star's bedside after he was found unconscious at a Nevada brothel.
